snippet.title: Ford Simulator 5 gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Ford Simulator 5, Dos PC game produced by Ford Motor Company in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/ford-simulator-5/4744/
